import requests
for url in [
    'https://cellxgene.cziscience.com/api/v0.5/datasets/21d3e683-80a4-4d9b-bc89-ebb2df513dde',
    'https://cellxgene.cziscience.com/api/v0.4/datasets/21d3e683-80a4-4d9b-bc89-ebb2df513dde',
    'https://cellxgene.cziscience.com/api/v1/datasets/21d3e683-80a4-4d9b-bc89-ebb2df513dde',
    'https://cellxgene.cziscience.com/api/v0.1/datasets/21d3e683-80a4-4d9b-bc89-ebb2df513dde',
]:
    try:
        r=requests.get(url, timeout=10)
        print(url, r.status_code, r.headers.get('content-type'))
        print(r.text[:200])
    except Exception as e:
        print(url, 'error', e)
